text:
> Ohio Janet Jackson, Chicago, The Cars nominated for rock hall FILE - In this Sept. 16, 2015, file photo, the group Los Lobos, from left, David Hidalgo, Louie Perez, Steve Berlin, Conrad Lozano and Cesar Rosas arrive at the Americana Music Honors and Awards show in Nashville, Tenn. The band is being considered for induction next year in the Rock and Roll Hall of Fame. (AP Photo/Mark Zaleski, File) The most compelling, sharable stories from across the web.
